Package com.refinedmods.refinedstorage2.api.storage.composite

Interface CompositeStorage<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of resource
All Superinterfaces:
ExtractableStorage<T>, InsertableStorage<T>, Storage<T>, StorageView<T>, TrackedStorage<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CompositeStorageImpl
@API(status=STABLE, since="2.0.0-milestone.1.0") public interface CompositeStorage<T> extends Storage<T>, TrackedStorage<T>
This represents a single storage that can be backed by multiple storages.
